data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this thoughtfully designed home in the vibrant community of Skyridge Valley in Clermont, FL. Built with attention to detail in 2000, this single-story gem boasts 1,908 square feet of living space that is both functional and inviting. The four bedrooms and two bathrooms offer ample room for families, couples, or anyone in search of a comfortable living space.  An open floor plan anchors the home, creating an inclusive environment for family activities and social gatherings. The central air conditioning ensures year-round comfort, while the new water heater provides reliable hot water on demand. In a blend of innovation and eco-conscious living, this home is equipped with a Tesla Powerwall, a remarkable feature that couples with solar panels to provide energy efficiency and backup. This integration not only ensures a constant energy supply but also actively reduces your utility expenses and carbon footprint, making this home a wise choice for the environmentally savvy.  The home's exterior features a low-maintenance asphalt shingle roof and sturdy concrete block construction with an attractive stucco finish. Step outside to discover a serene outdoor living area, complete with a screened swimming pool and a well-maintained sprinkler system that keeps the landscape lush and verdant.  Skyridge Valley is not just about the comfort of home but also about an active and engaging lifestyle. The community offers tennis courts, a basketball court, and a playground, perfect for enjoying Florida's sunny days.  Clermont, FL is a city on the rise, known for its scenic landscapes and a burgeoning economy. With its close proximity to renowned theme parks, residents can enjoy world-class entertainment within a short drive. The city itself offers a slice of tranquility with its picturesque hills and lakes, providing a perfect balance between urban and natural living.  This home in Skyridge Valley represents more than just a living space; it's a gateway to a life full of potential and adventure, offering all the amenities needed for a modern, active lifestyle. Whether you're taking a family trip to the nearby theme parks or enjoying a quiet evening in your poolside haven, this home is where your heart can settle and your life can flourish.
